lead_paragraph: Game Five of the World Series will be do-or-die for the Chicago Cubs but ace Jon Lester said he would treat Sunday's must-win start the same as any other game as his team tries to keep the Cleveland Indians from clinching the Fall Classic.

headline.print_headline: Do-or-Die but Still Business as Usual for Cubs Ace Lester
